          "type": "instant"
        }
      ],
      "entries": [
        "You rend a creature's vitality with a shadowy tendril and add it to your own. You force a creature within range that you can see to make a constitution saving throw, on a failed save they take {@damage 3d8} necrotic damage and you gain temporary hit points equal to the damage dealt. In addition, their hit point maximum is reduced by an amount equal to the damage they took. This reduction lasts for one hour. A {@spell remove curse} can end the effect early. On a success, they take half damage and their hit point maximum is not reduced."
      ],
      "entriesHigherLevel": [
        {
          "name": "At Higher Levels",
          "entries": [
            "When you cast this spell using a 3rd level or higher spell slot, the damage increases by {@damage 1d8} necrotic damage for each slot level above 2nd."
          ]
        }
